Package: ship-driver
Version: @VERSION@
Section: misc
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3, python3-serial, python3-paho-mqtt, mosquitto
Maintainer: Ilya Koptev <ilya.koptev@struhe.com>
Description: Ship-bus LoRa driver for Wiren Board
 Custom driver: owns the 4 MOD LoRa transmitters, talks Modbus to pwm8a04 + WB-UPS-v3,
 injects DFPlayer frames inline, runs a per-channel mode state machine and adaptive poll
 schedule, configures the LoRa modems, and mirrors everything to MQTT (boat1..4 + Ship Setup).
